description: Housewife Hot Dogs is a cart serving up delicious dogs to greater Seattle. They really bring the East Coast to the West with their authentic Sabrett brand dogs, a rare find on the Left Coast.  Housewife Hot Dogs caters both classics like the cream cheese dog, and more adventurous spins like the Hunger Husband- Cream Cheese, Bacon, Hash Browns, Grilled Onion, topped with a fried Egg.  Or how about The Nutty Housewife? Peanut Butter, Bacon and Grilled Onions. The Hormonal Housewife- Not sure what you want, a mix of whatever.
name: Housewife Hotdogs
